SUMMARY:Laces Out Run Club
DTSTAMP:20260618T101508Z
DTSTART:20260730T173000Z
DESCRIPTION:Every Thursday at 5:30 and 6:30 PM\, our Laces Out Run Club mem
	bers start on a route of their choosing\, ranging from a 2\, 3.5\, 5\, or 
	8 mile run. After their run\, they receive $2 off beers the rest of the ev
	ening! \nREWARDS \n🎽 10 runs: EH headband\n🎽 25 runs: Laces Out shirt\n🎽 5
	0 runs: Running shorts\n🎽 100 runs: Singlet \n  \n  \n  \n \n\nhttps://www
	.eurekaheights.com/event/laces-out-run-club-2025/2026-07-30/\n\nFrom Eurek
	a Heights Brewery
URL:https://www.eurekaheights.com/event/laces-out-run-club-2025/2026-07-30/
LOCATION:Tap Room\, 941 W 18TH ST.\, Houston\, TX\, 77008\, United States
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:eureka-heights-brew-co
CATEGORIES:Eureka Heights Brewery
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT1H
END:VEVENT
